f. The BAC to uphold utmost transparency in imparting fair play with the prospective 

bidders who could give the most advantageous terms and conditions to the City Government by posting notices and invitation to bid to the PhilGEPS;

g. The BAC to religiously invite observers, in the number prescribed by the law, in every session or meeting, in the absence of COA witnesses;

h. The BAC to conduct Pre-Bid and Pre-Procurement Conference, particularly those procurement or projects with material amounts;

i. The BAC to always uphold the strength of APP in complying the mode prescribed therein; and

